description: 밤하늘 아래 세 멤버가 모두 모여 서로의 손을 잡자, 그들의 중심에서 거대한 빛의 기둥이 하늘로 솟구칩니다. 루나(LUNA)가 대표로 카메라를 응시하며 'Shine on you'라고 속삭이듯 입모양을 합니다.
visual_concept: Night scene on a grassy hill under a starry sky. Three girls stand in a circle holding hands, radiating a soft inner glow. A beam of pure starlight erupts from their joined hands, illuminating the night. The central figure looks directly into the lens with a gentle, reassuring smile, wind blowing through her hair.
camera_movement: crane up starting from eye level to a high angle looking down at the light beam
lighting: Dark night background contrasted by a bright, divine white light emanating from the center of the group
